      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 12
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional find: a collector-grade vehicle that remains in showroom condition. This car has been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled garage and has never seen a drop of rain or snow. The exterior features original, flawless paint with a professional-grade ceramic coating that provides a deep, mirror-like finish. There are absolutely no door dings, rock chips, or scratches to be found. Inside, the cabin retains its 'new car' scent; the premium leather upholstery is supple and free of any creases, while the dashboard and trim remain pristine without a single blemish. Every electronic feature, from the premium sound system to the advanced navigation, functions exactly as it did the day it left the dealership. Mechanically, the vehicle is beyond reproach, boasting a full-service history performed exclusively by certified technicians. It rides on original alloy wheels with zero curb rash, wrapped in high-performance tires with ample tread. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that has been preserved with the utmost care and attention to detail.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
